constraints.search: (`setup_dm_constraints_search`) (index=_audit sourcetype=audittrail ((action=search search_id=*) OR info=terminate)) OR ( index=_internal AND ((sourcetype=scheduler app=*) OR (component=SearchProcessMemoryTracker) OR (sourcetype=splunkd component=DispatchManager username=* "QUEUED"))) OR (index=_introspection sourcetype=splunk_resource_usage component=PerProcess "data.process_type"=search "data.search_props.app"=*)

calculations.expression: IF(ISNULL(search) OR search="" OR match(trim(trim(search, "'")), "^\s*\|?\s*summarize") OR len(search) < 5, NULL(), trim(trim(search, "'")) )

IF(ISNULL(savedsearch_name) OR savedsearch_name=""  OR match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_|N\/A|^search\d+|\*") OR match(search, "^\| summarize") OR match(search_id, "^ta_\d+|^\d+"), "Undefined", savedsearch_name)
case ( ISNULL(user) OR user="", "Undefined", user="nobody", "system", match(user, "\*"), null(), true(), user )
IF ( ( ISNULL(roles) OR roles="") OR match(roles, "="), NULL(), trim(roles, "'"))

Case( 
    IsNum(search_et),search_et, 
    search_et="N/A" OR apiStartTime="N/A" OR match(apiStartTime,"_TIME"),0, 
    (IsNull(search_et) OR search_et="") AND IsNotNull(apiStartTime),strptime(apiStartTime,"%a %b %d %H:%M:%S %Y"),
    True(), Null())

Case( 
    IsNum(search_lt),search_lt,
    search_lt="N/A" OR apiEndTime="N/A" OR match(apiEndTime, "_TIME"),0, 
    (IsNull(search_lt) OR search_lt="") AND IsNotNull(apiEndTime),strptime(apiEndTime,"%a %b %d %H:%M:%S %Y"),
    True(), Null())

case ( 
      match(search_id1, "^SummaryDirector") OR match(search_id1, "^summarize_SummaryDirector") OR (match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_") AND NOT match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_DM_")), "report_acceleration",
      ( match(search_id1, "^DM_") OR match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_DM_") ), "datamodel_acceleration",
      match(search_id1, "^scheduler_") AND isnotnull(savedsearch_name) AND NOT match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_"), "scheduled", 
      match(search_id1, "^rt_"), "realtime", 
      match(search_id1, "^subsearch_"), "subsearch", 
      match(search_id1, "^ta_\d+"), "typeahead", 
      true(), "adhoc")
IF(ISNULL(emp_name) OR emp_name="" OR len(emp_name) > 50, NULL(), trim(emp_name, "'"))
case ( ISNOTNULL(search_id), search_id, ISNULL(sid) OR sid="", savedsearch_id, true(), sid )
IF(ISNULL(savedsearch_name) OR savedsearch_name=""  OR match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_"), "Undefined", savedsearch_name)

CASE ( 
    status2=="continued", "deferred",
    status2=="delegated", "delegated",
    status2=="delegated_scheduled", "delegated_scheduled",
    status2=="delegated_remote", "delegated_remote",
    status2=="delegated_remote_completion", "delegated_remote_completion",
    status2=="delegated_remote_error", "delegated_remote_error",
    status2=="delegated_waiting", "delegated_waiting",
    status2=="dispatched", "dispatched",
    status2=="max_pending", "max_pending",
    status2=="max_running", "max_running",
    status2=="skipped", "skipped",
    status2=="success", "completed",
    component="SearchProcessMemoryTracker", "terminated",
    component="DispatchManager", "queued",
    TRUE(), status2 )

CASE (
    info2="terminated", "terminated", 
    ISNULL(savedsearch_id) OR savedsearch_id="", "Undefined",
    TRUE(), savedsearch_id)
case ( ISNOTNULL(username), username, user="nobody", "system", ISNULL(user) OR user="", "Undefined", true(), user )
case ( ISNULL(window_time) OR window_time="", NULL(), window_time="-1", "auto", TRUE(), window_time )

case ( 
    match(alert_actions, "summary_index"), "summary_indexing",
    match(search_type, "scheduled"), "scheduled",
    match(_raw, "SavedSplunker") AND (isnotnull(savedsearch_name2) OR savedsearch_name2=""), "scheduled",
    match(search_type, "datamodel_acceleration"), "datamodel_acceleration",
    (search_id2 LIKE "DM_%" OR savedsearch_name2 LIKE "_ACCELERATE_DM%"), "datamodel_acceleration", 
    savedsearch_name2 LIKE "_ACCELERATE_DM%", "datamodel_acceleration",
    match(search_type, "report_acceleration"), "report_acceleration",
    match(search_id2, "^scheduler__") OR match(search_id2, "^scheduler__") , "scheduled",
    search_id2 LIKE "rt%", "realtime",
    search_id2 LIKE "subsearch%", "subsearch",
    (search_id2 LIKE "SummaryDirector%" OR search_id2 LIKE "summarize_SummaryDirector%"), "summary_director",
    true(), "adhoc")

constraints.search: (index=_internal AND ( (sourcetype=scheduler app=*) OR (component=SearchProcessMemoryTracker) OR (sourcetype=splunkd component=DispatchManager username=* "QUEUED")))

calculations.expression:
case ( isnotnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "peer", 'data.search_props.search_head', 
    isnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "head", "_self", 
    isnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "peer", "_unknown")

case ( 
    match('data.search_props.type', "ad-hoc"), "adhoc",
    match('data.search_props.type', "datamodel acceleration"), "datamodel_acceleration",
    match('data.search_props.type', "report acceleration"), "report_acceleration",
    match('data.search_props.type', "summary index"), "summary_indexing",
    true(), 'data.search_props.type')
